thors \\cite{AO14}, provides an improved upper bound\non the integrality gap of the natural LP relaxation of the Asymmetric Traveling\nSalesman Problem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Dec 2014 00:50:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Jul 2015 18:15:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-23"}
