putations for MM and beyond MM, and link one of these\ntechniques to some simple algorithms for inner product and summation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Dec 2014 01:00:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Dec 2014 14:07:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 5 Feb 2015 22:26:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-09"}
