 the LMC is $\\sim 4.5\n\\times 10^{-5} M_{\\odot}/yr$, the relative percentages due to C- and M- star\nbeing respectively 85$%$ and 15 $%$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Dec 2014 15:33:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-10"}
